    "title": "A magnificent gift from a dear friend neither forgotten nor forsaken.",
    "description": "Consumes 2 ammo per shot. Fires a miniature Butt Stallion that detonates on impact for roughly 150 percent gun damage in an area, then splits into 3 diamond projectiles that also explode on impact for about 70 percent grenade damage each. Swapping to the weapon plays a neigh."
