  "notes": "It can roll with any shotgun accessory, but no prefix is shown in the name. With a vertical grip, it fires 3 projectiles for the cost of 1, greatly increasing damage. The split projectiles deal about 70 percent of listed damage as splash and scale with grenade damage bonuses; their kills count as grenade kills (including Pull the Pin progress). Absorb shields do not absorb the explosions. Its special effect matches the SWORDSPLOSION!!!. It can only be claimed once per character.",
